        "created_at": "2026-01-11T22:08:05.807Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Please consider adding a PIN pad scrambling option for the app unlock feature in Signal.<br>\nThis would randomize the position of the numbers each time the PIN is entered, helping to prevent shoulder surfing and smudge attacks.</p>\n<p>I personally use this for my phone screen unlock and would love to see this as an option for Signal <em>(and any other apps supporting app lock on Android system lock).</em></p>\n<p>Since Signal prioritizes privacy, adding this small but meaningful protection would enhance security especially for users in high-risk environments.</p>\n<p>Would love to see this implemented!</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 6,
        "updated_at": "2026-01-11T22:15:19.386Z",
